es/193 km) to Fredericksburg, VA, and spend the night.\n\nDay 9: Fredericksburg, VA to Hershey, PA\n\n* Drive approximately 3 hours (170 miles/274 km) from Fredericksburg to Hershey, Pennsylvania.\n* Spend the day at Hersheypark, an amusement park with roller coasters, water rides, and a chocolate-themed experience.\n\nDay 10: Hershey, PA to Montreal\n\n* Drive approximately 7.5 hours (480 miles/772 km) from Hershey back to Montreal.\n\nNote: This plan is flexible, and you can adjust the activities or stops to suit your families' preferences. Make sure to check for any travel restrictions or requirements before your trip."
